reviews.text: Moderately priced place serving simple South Asian dishes. Pretty stomach filling stuff.

Newly opened, Karachi Hav a bite offers traditional Pakistani fare in the heart of Kwai Chung. The place is air conditioned and has diner-esque seating. The biryani here is authentic Karachi style.

They also offer some Turkish kebab as well as pizza. Goes without saying that all the food served here is halal.
An awesome location for all types of Meal Parties, love it to visit again.
